# sched/series — CPU scheduler patches
# Enable with: ENABLE_CACHY=1
#
# Upstream status: The cacule scheduler was removed from XanMod upstream
# and was never accepted into mainline Linux. The BORE scheduler
# (Burst-Oriented Response Enhancer) is the current recommended
# alternative and is included in recent XanMod releases natively.
#
# For 6.x targets, consider using XanMod's built-in BORE scheduler
# instead of enabling ENABLE_CACHY=1.
#
# Uncomment only if you have a verified 6.x-compatible cacule patch:
# 001-cachy-scheduler.patch
